{
  "stem": "2980.2",
  "chunk_idx": 2,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 5.5,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "And she would come in-- [SPEAKING GERMAN].",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "And the [SPEAKING GERMAN].",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "And they would teach us German.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "And then they would teach us Ukrainian all of a sudden.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "And we would have Russian.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "And they would teach us Russian.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 13,
      "text": "In Yiddish, they start teaching us also about the-- not Jewish history, but the history of workers and what happened in Russia and Sholem Aleichem.",
      "word_count": 25
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 14,
      "text": "And we were still children.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 15,
      "text": "We were not grown-up.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 11,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "It was in-- was in '39.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 11,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "It was-- I was 10 years-- 10, 11.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 11,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "At that point, they-- we started-- start teaching us math and some physics and other things-- these subjects I liked-- and Russian poetry, and other things.",
      "word_count": 26
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 11,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And so, so we really had loaded up our time.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 11,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "And the school time was extended.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 11,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "There was no more cheder, no more going to shul.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 11,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "We have to come to, to school Shabbos, Saturday.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 11,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "We had to go.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 11,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "That was, for us, terrible.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 11,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "But they specifically made sure that we go Saturday to school.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 11,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "And my father had to work on Saturday for, for the--",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "To school--",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 13,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "--not to shul.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 13,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "My father had to go to work also.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 13,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "They forced the Jews to work on Shabbos also.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "[SIGHS] Those who were very Orthodox-- either they didn't work, so they-- it was a danger.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "You had to work.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "Everybody was a worker.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "Whoever was not a worker-- they made lists of people who were merchants before the war, and they shipped them out to Siberia.",
      "word_count": 23
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "They were called leeches of society.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "So my father was, even though it was his machine shop and works, and so on, we, we might have been considered leeches of society, also.",
      "word_count": 26
    }
  ],
